            <span class="text-emerald-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">One product vs. twelve doesn't affect conversion</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Store A: 3 products. Conversion: 2.8%. Store B: 47 products. Conversion: 2.9%. Catalog size doesn't matter for conversion. Product quality and site trust do.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-emerald-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">AI builder stores migrate to Shopify in 11 months avg</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Tracked 23 stores starting on Squarespace/Wix. After 11 months: 19 (83%) migrated to Shopify. E-commerce needs outgrow AI builders. Start cheap, plan migration.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

