      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-green-50 border-[3px] border-emerald-400 p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Real E-commerce Store Launch Stories: 12-Month Outcomes</h2>
